<h2>About v12.9.0 Update</h2>

<!-- update-description-begin -->
<ul>
<li>‚ú® New Features

<ul>
<li><code>Open config folder</code> button has been added into Preferences.<br>
The feature provides <a href="https://pqrs.org/osx/karabiner/document.html#export">an easy way exporting configuration</a>.</li>
</ul></li>
<li>‚ö°Ô∏è Improvements

<ul>
<li>Added a workaround for non-dismissible <code>Device is ignored temporarily</code> alert
which is caused by some devices that sends abnormal input events.</li>
</ul></li>
<li>üêõ Bug Fixes

<ul>
<li>Fixed <code>Add {key_code} to Karabiner-Elements</code> button on EventViewer for unnamed keys (raw number key codes).</li>
<li>Fixed an issue that modifier flag events are not dispatched when changing pointing button while other character keys are pressed.<br>
(e.g., when changing pointing_button::button3 -&gt; command+pointing_button::button1, command modifier is not sent when button1 is pressed while <code>t</code> key is also pressed.)</li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<!-- update-description-end -->
<p>
